text:
Yuika, why don't you join us?
This umbrella is big.

Oh, really?
Is it okay for Mitsumine to intrude on such a prime spot?

Oh wow, you're right.
There's still plenty of room even with both of us in!

I got this from Mamimi the other day
when we were working together.

She said she bought it on the way here,
but then the rain stopped on the way back.
She said we could use one of the umbrellas at the dorm.
